Package: libcasacore-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libcasacore1 (= ${binary:Version}), wcslib-dev
Description: A set of libraries derived from aips++
 This project contains c++ libraries which were the
 code of the discontinued aips++ package.

